page.title: 15DAY IN LIFE MICHELLE CHAFER
page.content: I usually get up at 6.55 get washed dressed and eat Weetabix and tea for breakfast.7.55 played on computer. 8.30 to school,played with friends, clapping games.9.00 register,maths investigations.Assembly, break,then Domesday work, Life in the castle. 12.00 lunch; roast beef,carrots,beans roast pototoes,cake and custard. 13.15 silent reading,drawing,painting break the story The Ice Palace. School finised 15.15. Home for organ practice, swimming exercises of press ups, squat thrusts. 16.40 to dancing lesson for tap and ballet. 18.30 to Barnsley for swimming train ing, finished 21.00 hours. Home for 21.50 read, then went to bed at 22.39.
